title: The Track 9 Rankings
description:
A listener confessed that they always thought that Taylor's track 9s were her most emotional songs and suggested that we rank those.. so we did! Most of us took all of her track 9s, thought long and hard about our choices, and then ranked them accordingly. Someone's list turned out a little different than the rest.. and yes, minor fights ensued.
What would you like to hear from us? Let us know, and we just might do it! There's lots of ways to contact us!
